        <p>We offer a variety of services, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Borrowing and returning books</li>
            <li>Access to e-books and digital resources</li>
            <li>Reading programs and events for all ages</li>
            <li>Community outreach and engagement</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Facilities</h4>
        <p>Our library provides comfortable reading areas, study spaces, and computer facilities. We strive to create an atmosphere that encourages exploration and learning.</p>

        <h4>Events and Programs</h4>
        <p>Stay tuned for our upcoming events and programs, including book clubs, author talks, and educational workshops. We believe in creating a sense of community through shared literary experiences.</p>
